The video of a man in Police uniform is trending on Twitter. Tweeted by @Gidi_Traffic on Tuesday, the man is seen reeling back and forth in the flood and appears unstable. An individual in mufti is seen trying to sustain and prevent him from plunging headlong into the torrent. @Gidi_Traffic is convinced that the man is drunk, but it has not been able to provide the exact scene of the incident or confirm the identity of the man. @Gidi_Traffic had tweeted: “A drunk Policeman endangering his life in the flood.” See the video, courtesy @Gidi_Traffic: